    "on_demand_info_mrDTy9": {
      "type": "on-demand-info",
      "blocks": {
        "info_block_xAxwyD": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Adaptogens: help your body handle stress",
            "text": "<p>\"Adaptogen\" just means a natural ingredient that helps your body deal with stress instead of adding to it. We use <strong>ashwagandha</strong> and <strong>ginseng</strong> — plants people have leaned on for centuries. In simple terms: they help you stay calm and steady when the day gets loud, so your focus doesn't get hijacked by a racing mind.</p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8495bfd7-cd1b-43ed-852f-5f64b8bddc7c-2026-07-18.png",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "info_block_gneeJw": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Nootropics: support how you think and remember",
            "text": "<p>\"Nootropic\" is just a fancy word for something that supports your brain — focus, memory, mental clarity. We use <strong>bacopa</strong> (long known as the \"student's herb\" for supporting memory), <strong>ginkgo</strong> (known for supporting healthy blood flow to the brain), and <strong>L-tyrosine</strong> (which supports focus when you're under pressure). No magic, no hype — just ingredients chosen because they earn their spot.</p>",
            "media_type": "mixed_media",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/96ed3d1a-8dcb-4c51-b15c-133721a01b2c-2026-07-18.png",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "info_block_KfeYGt": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why a drink instead of a pill?",
            "text": "<p>Pills and powders are easy to forget and easy to skip. A cold, actually-tasty drink is something you look forward to — so you'll actually use it. And because it's a liquid, there's nothing to choke down or mix up. Crack, sip, done.</p><p><strong>Our rule: enough to work, not enough to overload</strong></p><p>More isn't better — it's just more. We dose our ingredients so they absorb well and build up in your system over time, without the \"too much\" feeling. That's why you get clean energy, not a chemical buzz.</p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4a63829b-7dbf-4120-ac39-52df4faf515e-2026-07-18.png",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "info_block_Mra9qW": {
          "type": "info_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "So what actually makes BRAiNLUBE different?",
            "text": "<p>Here's the honest breakdown:</p><ul><li><strong>A regular energy drink</strong> gives you a big hit of synthetic caffeine and sugar. You spike, then you crash — and it does nothing for focus.</li><li><strong>Coffee</strong> gives you caffeine and not much else. Great, until the jitters and the afternoon slump show up.</li><li><strong>Focus pills and powders</strong> might have the good ingredients, but they're a chore, they taste like nothing, and you stop using them.</li><li><strong>BRAiNLUBE</strong> brings the focus ingredients, the calm ingredients, and just-enough clean caffeine together — in a drink you'll actually reach for. Energy that shows up, focus that sticks, and no crash waiting on the other side.</li></ul>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ed5dcad2-1517-4abd-a5b7-4c9614419ec8-2026-07-18.jpg",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        }
      },
